122@dataclass_json
123@dataclass
124class Metadata:
125    transaction_key: str = ""
126    request_id: str = ""
127    sha256: str = ""
128    created: str = ""
129    duration: float = 0
130    channels: int = 0
131    models: Optional[List[str]] = field(
132        default=None, metadata=config(exclude=lambda f: f is None)
133    )
134    warnings: Optional[List[Warning]] = field(
135        default=None, metadata=config(exclude=lambda f: f is None)
136    )
137    model_info: Optional[Dict[str, ModelInfo]] = field(
138        default=None, metadata=config(exclude=lambda f: f is None)
139    )
140    summary_info: Optional[SummaryInfo] = field(
141        default=None, metadata=config(exclude=lambda f: f is None)
142    )
143    intents_info: Optional[IntentsInfo] = field(
144        default=None, metadata=config(exclude=lambda f: f is None)
145    )
146    sentiment_info: Optional[SentimentInfo] = field(
147        default=None, metadata=config(exclude=lambda f: f is None)
148    )
149    topics_info: Optional[TopicsInfo] = field(
150        default=None, metadata=config(exclude=lambda f: f is None)
151    )
152    extra: Optional[Dict] = field(
153        default=None, metadata=config(exclude=lambda f: f is None)
154    )
155
156    def __getitem__(self, key):
157        _dict = self.to_dict()
158        if "models" in _dict:
159            _dict["models"] = [str(models) for models in _dict["models"]]
160        if "warnings" in _dict:
161            _dict["warnings"] = [
162                Warning.from_dict(warnings) for warnings in _dict["warnings"]
163            ]
164        if "model_info" in _dict:
165            _dict["model_info"] = [
166                ModelInfo.from_dict(model_info)
167                for _, model_info in _dict["model_info"].items()
168            ]
169        if "summary_info" in _dict:
170            _dict["summary_info"] = SummaryInfo.from_dict(_dict["summary_info"])
171        if "intents_info" in _dict:
172            _dict["intents_info"] = IntentsInfo.from_dict(_dict["intents_info"])
173        if "sentiment_info" in _dict:
174            _dict["sentiment_info"] = SentimentInfo.from_dict(_dict["sentiment_info"])
175        if "topics_info" in _dict:
176            _dict["topics_info"] = TopicsInfo.from_dict(_dict["topics_info"])
177        if "extra" in _dict:
178            _dict["extra"] = [str(extra) for _, extra in _dict["extra"].items()]
179        return _dict[key]
180
181    def __setitem__(self, key, val):
182        self.__dict__[key] = val
183
184    def __str__(self) -> str:
185        return self.to_json(indent=4)
